exportQueryAnswersToCsv(PositiveLiteral, String, boolean) - Method in interface org.semanticweb.vlog4j.core.reasoner.Reasoner
Evaluates an atomic query (query) on the implicit facts loaded into the reasoner and the explicit facts materialised by the reasoner, and writes its answers the .csv file at given path csvFilePath:
An answer to the query is the terms a fact that matches the query: the fact predicate is the same as the query predicate, the TermType.CONSTANT terms of the query appear in the answer fact at the same term position, and the TermType.VARIABLE terms of the query are matched by terms in the fact, either named (TermType.CONSTANT) or anonymous (TermType.BLANK).
